rows.label: qst101409_msg001
rows.name: もっとでかいものに襲われたっぽいね(仮)

rows.label: qst101409_msg002
rows.name: FS追跡で追跡してみよう

rows.label: qst101409_msg101
rows.name: やったね(仮)

rows.label: qst101409_msg201
rows.name: 足りなかった(仮)

rows.label: qst101409_msg0001
rows.name:
It's a Volff...
Looks like something attacked it.

rows.label: qst101409_msg0002
rows.name:
Check it out, more tracks...
Bigger ones this time.

rows.label: qst101409_msg0003
rows.name:
We should be able to follow.
No time to lose.

rows.label: qst101409_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't think we can follow them
very far, though...

rows.label: qst101409_msg0101
rows.name:
A dead Volff...
Something musta got it.

rows.label: qst101409_msg0102
rows.name:
Aha! More tracks.
Big ones, at that.

rows.label: qst101409_msg0103
rows.name:
Let's follow them!
And hurry!

rows.label: qst101409_msg0104
rows.name: Ah, the trail stops short though...

rows.label: qst101409_msg0201
rows.name:
Oh, a Volff?
I wonder what got it...

rows.label: qst101409_msg0202
rows.name:
More tracks!
Ooh, looks like a whopper.

rows.label: qst101409_msg0203
rows.name:
We should be able to track 'em.
Well? What're we waiting for!

rows.label: qst101409_msg0204
rows.name:
But I'm not liking our chances
of tracking it down...

rows.label: qst101409_msg0301
rows.name:
Meh-meh...is Volff!
Hunter become hunted, yes?

rows.label: qst101409_msg0302
rows.name:
Ooh, and more tracks!
This time big tracks!

rows.label: qst101409_msg0303
rows.name:
How about we follow tracks,
see where creature go?

rows.label: qst101409_msg0304
rows.name:
Meh-meh-mehhh...
Could not follow tracks...

rows.label: qst101409_msg0401
rows.name:
A Volff carcass...
But who was the assailant?

rows.label: qst101409_msg0402
rows.name:
There are more tracks here.
Larger than before...

rows.label: qst101409_msg0403
rows.name:
We can follow them.
Let's not tarry.

rows.label: qst101409_msg0404
rows.name: We've lost the trail...
